text: Bachelor Lake may refer to: * Bachelor Lake (Lac Bachelor), in Quebec, Canada, a lake in the same drainage basin as Lake Waswanipi in Nord-du-Québec * Bachelor Lake, a small lake near Live Oak, Florida, U.S. * Bachelor Lake, in Aitkin County, Minnesota near Farm Island Township, U.S. * Bachelor Lake (Brown County, Minnesota), U.S. ==See also== * Bachelor's Lake in the Hiawatha National Forest in Michigan, U.S. ==References==
title: Bachelor Lake
